<section class="inaction">
  <div class="inaction-inner">
    <div class="inaction-label">
      <span class="label">The Cost of Inaction</span>
    </div>
    <div class="inaction-body">
      <h2 class="inaction-title">
        THE LONGER<br/>
        YOU WAIT,<br/>
        THE MORE<br/>
        <span class="accent">IT COSTS</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="inaction-text">
        <p>
          Inefficient internal tooling is not a static problem. As your
          organization grows, the friction scales with it. What takes one
          team an extra hour today takes ten teams an extra hour tomorrow.
        </p>
        <p>
          The organizations that build the right internal infrastructure
          early gain a compounding operational advantage. Those that defer
          the investment find themselves managing increasingly complex
          workarounds while competitors move faster with less friction.
        </p>
        <p class="inaction-closer">
          The question is not whether your operations need better tooling.
          It is how long inefficiency will be tolerated before it becomes
          a strategic liability.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .inaction {
    border-bottom: var(--border);
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .inaction-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
  }

  .inaction-label {
    writing-mode: vertical-lr;
    transform: rotate(180deg);
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space);
    border-right: 4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .inaction-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }

  .inaction-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-h2);
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    border-right: 4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .inaction-title .accent {
    color: var(--color-bg);
    -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--color-bg);
    color: transparent;
  }

  .inaction-text {
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space);
  }

  .inaction-text p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .inaction-closer {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1rem !important;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1.3 !important;
    border-top: 4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    padding-top: var(--space);
    margin-top: var(--space);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .inaction-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .inaction-label { writing-mode: horizontal-tb; transform: none; border-right: none; border-bottom: 4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
    .inaction-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .inaction-title { border-right: none; border-bottom: 4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); padding: var(--space-lg); }
    .inaction-text { padding: var(--space-lg); }
  }
</style>
